      <title>美国司法部就 iPhone 反垄断案起诉苹果公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-justice-department-sues-apple-in-antitrust-case-over-iphone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部和 16 名总检察长周四起诉苹果公司，指控这家 iPhone 制造商阻止竞争对手访问其热门设备上的硬件和软件功能，违反了反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/us-justice-department-sues-apple-in-antitrust-case-over-iphone</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:31:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯在发射前几秒取消了国际空间站机组人员的太空发射</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/russia-cancels-space-launch-with-iss-crew-seconds-before-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据国际文传电讯社援引俄罗斯联邦航天局的广播报道，俄罗斯取消了联盟号火箭的发射，该火箭将在国际空间站起飞前运送宇航员前往国际空间站。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/russia-cancels-space-launch-with-iss-crew-seconds-before-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:20:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腾讯将加大中东云投资，推动地区人工智能发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/tencent-to-boost-mideast-cloud-investments-amid-regional-ai-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[腾讯控股有限公司正在寻求扩大其在沙特阿拉伯和阿拉伯联合酋长国的云业务，因为该公司押注，重点发展中东人工智能等产业将需要在数据存储方面进行巨额新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/tencent-to-boost-mideast-cloud-investments-amid-regional-ai-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:16:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊送货竞争对手为美国扩张获得新资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/amazon-delivery-rival-secures-fresh-funding-for-us-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[电子商务物流初创公司 Pandion –这有助于萨克斯第五大道 (Saks Fifth Avenue) 等零售商与亚马逊 (Amazon.com Inc.) 的快速送货服务展开竞争——已获得 4150 万美元的新资金以扩大其业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/amazon-delivery-rival-secures-fresh-funding-for-us-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩尔茨得到 ISS 的支持，商界领袖参与迪士尼之战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳尔逊·佩尔茨 (Nelson Peltz) 在加入娱乐公司华特迪士尼公司 (Walt Disney Co.) 董事会的过程中得到了一家有影响力的股东咨询公司和一群商界领袖的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/peltz-backed-to-improve-disney-by-group-of-business-leaders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:59:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>月球着陆器制造商直观机器超出销售预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/moon-lander-maker-intuitive-machines-beats-sales-expectations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Intuitive Machines Inc.上季度的销售预期超过了华尔街的预期，这对最近因在月球上登陆航天器而声名鹊起的公司来说是又一提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/moon-lander-maker-intuitive-machines-beats-sales-expectations</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:56:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果首席执行官在上海开设新店，展现对中国的承诺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/apple-ceo-opens-new-shanghai-store-in-show-of-china-commitment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司首席执行官蒂姆·库克周四在上海市中心开设了一家大型新店，表明该公司致力于将中国作为市场和生产基地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/apple-ceo-opens-new-shanghai-store-in-show-of-china-commitment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 11:38:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice France 贷款机构正在与 Houlihan 合作制定债务计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/altice-france-creditors-are-working-on-a-debt-plan-with-houlihan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice France 的债权人已开始与财务和法律顾问合作，贷款人正在准备与该公司就债务问题展开潜在的斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/altice-france-creditors-are-working-on-a-debt-plan-with-houlihan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 09:49:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
